For comprehensive help, see our website. But this list
of commands will you started.
n, s, e, w, u, d        Go north, south, east, west, up, and down.
flee                    Try to escape from combat.
i                       Inventory.
stat                    List your attributes.
skills                  List your skills.
kill <obj>              Attack the <obj>.
look                    Look around you.
look <obj>              Look at an object.
look in <obj>           Look inside an object.
get <obj>               Pick something up.
get from <obj1> <obj2>  Get <obj2> out of <obj1>.
drop <obj>              Drop something.
drop in <obj1> <obj2>   Put <obj2> into <obj1>.
-- Note that look in, get from, and drop in
-- don't work on objects in your inventory!
-- You have to drop the container before
-- mucking around inside of it.
stow <obj>              Return <obj> to inventory. 
wield <obj>             Use <obj> as a weapon.
hold <obj>              Hold <obj> in your off hand.
wear <obj>              Wear <obj> on your person.
-- Dropping or stowing and object is the same as
-- taking it off your body or ceasing to wield or
-- hold it.
sneak, nosneak          Start and stop sneaking.
short                   Toggle short descriptions.
quit                    Exit the mud.
swindle <mark> <item>   Try to swindle someone.